---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Blog">
  <div class="blog-post card">
    <div class="blog-header">
      <h2>I am so grateful...</h2>
      <span class="blog-date">March 2026</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="blog-content">
      <div class="image-placeholder blog-feature">
        <span>[Photo of New Home or Graduation Here]</span>
      </div>
      <p>I am so grateful for the blessings I have been given in this lifetime. Both my children are about to graduate, I'm finally a homeowner [Yay!], and ***** Eye Care has provided me the perfect environment...</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .blog-post { padding: 2rem; border-bottom: 5px solid var(--accent-blue); }
  .blog-feature { width: 100%; height: 300px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; }
  .blog-header h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: var(--primary-blue); }
  .blog-content p { font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #4a5568; }
</style>
